	build-essential \
	libserd-dev \
	sqlite3 \
	libsqlite3-dev \

COPY Sources Sources
COPY Tests Tests
COPY rdf-tests rdf-tests
RUN swift build

ENV KINEO_W3C_TEST_PATH /work/rdf-tests
CMD ["swift", "test", "--parallel"]
